{"type":"message","id":"6801ad6f","parentId":"0067f6f7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:28:25.845Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-30 09:28 GMT+2] Design the complete Sierra Blu Realty employee/admin system in Figma only, using Stitch if available. Do not write code. Do not create a repo. Do not build a separate prototype outside Figma.\n\nBrand:\n- Sierra Blu Realty\n- Beyond Brokerage\n- Smart Decisions, AI-Driven\n- Preserve the official Sierra Blu logo exactly as approved\n\nRequired screens:\nLogin, Dashboard, Units List, Add Unit, Unit Editor, Projects List, Project Editor, Developers List, Developer Editor, Clients / Leads, Requests List, Request Detail, Recommendations, Viewings List, Viewing Detail, Content Hub, Homepage Content Editor, About Editor, Services Editor, Contact Editor, Careers Editor, Media Library, Featured Media, Sync Center, Property Finder Sync, Dedupe Queue, Settings, System Kit.\n\nNavigation groups:\n- Operations\n- Content\n- Assets & Sync\n\nNon-negotiable product rules:\n- Firestore is the source of truth\n- Property Finder sync must be visible in the UI\n- Hybrid inventory must be supported\n- Manual/editorial overrides must remain visible and never be silently overwritten\n- UI must expose source state, sync state, override state, visibility state, and media state\n- Units screens must show operational badges for source, sync, override, visibility, media, and Property Finder status\n- Safe sync review flow is required\n- Dedupe queue is required\n- Content Hub is a core product area\n- Media Library and Featured Media are real internal screens\n- Settings and System Kit must be real reusable parts of the system\n\nDesign requirements:\n- English + Arabic\n- Proper LTR + RTL\n- Desktop + mobile variants\n- Reusable components, variables, styles, auto layout\n- Clean premium internal product UI, not a generic dashboard\n- Keep it implementation-ready\n\nDeliver:\n1. Main pages/frames in Figma\n2. Reusable design system / System Kit\n3. Component variants\n4. Clear naming for screens and components\n5. Note what is still missing only if blocked by absent logo/Figma source"}],"timestamp":1774855705840}}
