uardrails so it stays implementation-ready and premium\n\n3. **Do both**\n   - full product UX spec\n   - plus the exact prompt sequence to use in Stitch/Figma\n\nIf you send me:\n- the **approved logo asset** (`svg/png/pdf/fig`)\n- and ideally a **Figma file link or source structure**\n  \nI can make the output much tighter and handoff-ready.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08c5e391118130a30169ca27c14e0c81918454f7b46758ab0e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":14361,"output":745,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15106,"cost":{"input":0.035902500000000004,"output":0.011175000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04707750000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774856116349,"responseId":"resp_08c5e391118130a30169ca27b5433c819192f5e8bd58662383"}}
