{"type":"message","id":"0a4eb952","parentId":"cc005992","timestamp":"2026-03-30T10:00:59.571Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-30 11:31:23 GMT+2] What I noticed:\nSystem: The OpenClaw gateway service configuration is out of date or non-standard. The service command does not include the `gateway` subcommand, and the gateway is configured as loopback-only, meaning only local clients can connect.\nSystem: \nSystem: Why it matters:\nSystem: This configuration issue prevents external clients, such as Telegram, from connecting to the OpenClaw gateway. This directly impacts Sierra Blu Realty's ability to serve clients through its primary communication channels.\nSystem: \nSystem: Recommended next step:\nSystem: Run `openclaw doctor --repair` to fix the gateway service configuration and enable external connectivity. I can take care of this next.\nSystem: [2026-03-30 11:45:22 GMT+2] What I noticed\nSystem: The OpenClaw Gateway service configuration appears to be outdated or non-standard. Specifically, the service command is missing the `gateway` subcommand, and the gateway is currently configured for loopback-only operation. There are no recent client-facing sessions visible beyond this internal operations check.\nSystem: \nSystem: Why it matters\nSystem: This configuration issue is critical because it likely prevents external services, such as Telegram and WhatsApp, from connecting to OpenClaw. If external clients cannot connect, Sierra cannot function as a private real estate concierge, effectively blocking all incoming client interactions. The absence of recent client sessions could be a symptom of this core connectivity problem.\nSystem: \nSystem: Recommended next step\nSystem: I recommend running `openclaw doctor --repair` immediately to correct the gateway service configuration, followed by `openclaw gateway restart` to apply the changes. I can handle this next if you'd like.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/sierr/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026 — 11:59 AM (Africa/Cairo) / 2026-03-30 09:59 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774864859518}}
